media-staging-import - Media Staging Import

USAGE:
    media-staging-import <date-name>

DESCRIPTION:
    Import media from DCIM to staging area with proper directory
    structure. Mounts device, moves files, sets permissions, and unmounts.

ARGUMENTS:
    date-name
        Date path in format: 2021-2030/2025/01.January/15.0.snow-forts
        (decade/year/month.day-event-name)

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-media-mountpoint PATH
        Media mountpoint directory

    -conf-media-user USER
        Media file owner

NOTE:
    Requires root privileges.

EXAMPLES:
    media-staging-import "2021-2030/2025/01.January/15.0.snow-forts"
    media-staging-import "2011-2020/2019/12.December/25.0.christmas"
